The mutation surface extends beyond the Quality UI: production output QA, warehouse LP QA/blocking, inspections, cold-chain/CCP automation, and database triggers all touch the same state. I’m now checking those writers against the canonical hold schema and site-scoping migrations, with special attention to multi-hold release behavior.
